official_title: Faith in Action! A Cluster-Randomized Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy of a Church-based Navigation Model to Increase Breast Cancer Screening Among Korean Women in Los Angeles
inclusion_criteria:
* Korean woman who is 45 years or older
* Does not currently have a breast cancer diagnosis
* Non-adherent to cancer screening (did not receive mammogram in last 2 years based on self-report)
* Prospective or current member of participating Korean Churches
* Willing to participate in study
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 45 Years
Must have maximum age of 80 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Does not meet inclusion criteria as described above
